Rating: 4
This was incredibly delicious, even though my tastes trend toward carbonara over healthy stuff. I added a half cup of sun-dried tomatoes, but I tried it before adding them and it was still tasty. I used coarse bulgur and French green lentils, which I think really make a difference here. The best part of this salad was the texture. The combination of ingredients gives it an addictive crunch, which made it hard to put down.

