Rating: 4
We love this elegant, subtle salad. I've made it for years. I usually add a bit more tarragon vinegar and fresh herbs; you can also add a little more olive oil if it's dry. French green lentils are essential. This is not a cook-out salad -- nicer with fish or lighter meats or as part of a salad buffet.

