Rating: 4
This is great and my 4 year old loves it! I chop the carrots fine and increase the amount. Definitely do not use brown lentils; the french green lentils keep the salad from becoming mushy. Like all vinegar-based salads, the "edge" comes off it if it sits overnight. Great the next day.

